        <updateDate>2019-09-19T17:16:29Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Hurricane Dorian Charitable Giving Act</b></p> <p>This bill suspends limitations on the tax deduction for charitable contributions in the case of cash contributions made for relief efforts related to Hurricane Dorian. Such contributions must be made after August 23, 2019, and before January 1, 2020, for such relief efforts.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
